# Node.py

Run nodejs from python

## Features

- Runs: .js, .ts, .mjs and .cjs files.
- Supports all npm libraries
- Automatically compiles .ts files and runs them with NO tsconfig (uses tsc)
- No dependencies
- Uses modern api

